sequenceDiagram
    actor Human
    actor Agent
    participant API as agent-tasks API
    participant Inbox as Signal inbox
    participant Audit as Audit log

    Note over Human,Audit: 1. Human creates a task
    Human->>API: POST /api/projects/{id}/tasks
    API->>Audit: task.created
    opt task is review-bound or assigned
        API->>Inbox: emit task_assigned signal
    end

    Note over Agent,Audit: 2. Agent picks up work
    Agent->>API: task_pickup
    API-->>Agent: { kind: "signal" | "review" | "work" | "idle", ... }
    Note right of API: v2 inlines pending signals + reviews<br/>into one call; signals_poll is legacy-only

    Note over Agent,Audit: 3. Agent claims + reads instructions
    Agent->>API: task_start { taskId }
    API->>API: confidence + dependency gates
    alt below threshold
        API-->>Agent: 422 confidence_below_threshold
    else gates pass
        API->>Audit: task.transitioned (open to in_progress)
        API-->>Agent: { task, instructions, allowedTransitions }
    end
